values:
So, College is interesting. Let me just tell you Nova is so easy. 
   I am taking History- the prof. talks the whole time while we take notes and thats it.
   Sociology- interesting, the professor is extremely opinionated but at least we know were he stands i guess. I have to read a book called The Demon Haunted World (A Candle in the Dark) it is incredibly boring in the beginning but its getting better. The title is cool though. 
   Liberal Arts Math- really easy so far, if you are bad in math this class is great. There are so many math problems for homework though. Thats the only bad thing so far. 
   Art History- Mrs. Lash is great, she is very funny. We just run through a chapter of the humongous book every class while looking at cave paintings, so far. The only thing i don't like about this class is that you have to do a presentation...I hate them so much, I don't see what the point of doing them is. 
   That's all of the classes I am taking, only four this semester. Amber is in all of my classes so we carpool each other. The problem with signing up for all of the same classes with Amber is that I have her to talk to so i haven't really met to many other people. 
   My best friend Megan is off at ECU, she likes it there but has a lot of projects and stuff. And Jordyn is in Utah, I miss them...

ok so today i got my wisdom teeth pulled out, they gave me so many shots of novicane it isn't funny. Luckally i couldn't feel anything after that and i chose to be awake while they did it, don't ask me why, man my mouth hurts right now! anyway they only part i didn't watch was when the dentist told me to close my eyes cause he was sewing up my gums were we pulled out my teeth, i had 4 removed. After it was done they stuffed my cheeks with gaws, i looked like a chipmunk or as jen puts it ren from Even Stevens when her cheeks got all puff after she got her braces off. The nurse or dentist's assistant or whatever you call her asked me if i wanted to see my teeth, i shook my head no, i would prefer not to, she said they looked like dice... so now i am hunger but everytime i try to eat something like pudding or ice cream it hurts soo bad just to swallow so i think i would rather put up with my stomach grumbling that all that pain, it really sucks. The medicine helps a bit though so i don't feel to bad, i guess. Zsazsa i think or i hope i will be up to going to your party, i really want to go. Thanx again everyone for the comments :) you guys are the best. I think i will go rest so i can recover. Jorydn i posted the address to the website i got the pick from on the last entry in the comments thing.
